{"id":288793,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/【图说天朝】根正苗红/","date":"2013-04-12T07:29:24Z","modified":"2014-12-31T02:00:26Z","title":"【图说天朝】根正苗红","content":"<p>近日，人民日报在建新大楼的照片在网络上广为流传，网友纷纷称其“造型别致”。有网友称：人民日报社新办公楼造型很特别，是一个球体变形后削去三个面，变成三面凹进的体量，混凝土框架与大型横梁结构的超高层，预计2014年完全竣工。</p>\n<p>该大楼与遥相呼应的央视大楼的合成图一同在网络上不断被转载，被网友揶揄为“阳具配裤衩”。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248389_159611.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-288794\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248389_159611.jpg\" alt=\"37787_248389_159611\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248389_159611.jpg 818w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248389_159611-300x226.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 818px) 100vw, 818px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">因在建大楼顶部几层被覆盖脚手架 故而“造型别致”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248391_641634.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-288795\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248391_641634.jpg\" alt=\"37787_248391_641634\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248391_641634.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/37787_248391_641634-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">下图为网友PS作品</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-288796\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1.jpg\" alt=\"1304112343182320--ss1\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1.jpg 350w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/1304112343182320-ss1-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[9807,22741,26561,9149]}